overview: Beautiful, seasoned stunners become the objects of desire for young, vulnerable girls. Pretty professional Vanna Bardot longs to do more than work under boss Kayla Paige. Pretty renter Paige Owens puts the moves on landlord Aiden Ashley. Birthday girl Jane Wilde is rubbed the right way by masseuse London River. Khloe Kapri has a breakthrough with lesbian psychologist Ryan Keely.
title: Women Loving Girls 4
